# Project workflow

- Read `CLAUDE.md` at the repo root first.
- Use `make setup` on first clone, then `make dev` for local development.
- Use `make test` or `make verify` before finishing a task.
- Never commit `.env` — copy from `.env.example` when needed.
- Keep changes scoped to what the user asked for.
